  "instructions": [
    "heat coconut oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add chicken to the skillet and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "add onion, garlic, and ginger to the skillet and cook until the onion is translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "add barbeque sauce to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "bring the sauce to a simmer and cook for 2-3 minutes or until thickened.",
    "add tadka spice mix, salt, and black pepper to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "reduce heat to low and let the chicken cook in the sauce for an additional 5-7 minutes or until cooked through.",
    "garnish with green onions and fresh cilantro.",
    "serve hot and enjoy!"
  ],
